$interpreted: Hestia: Uwah~ Oww, so I did get injured in the fight back there after all...
Hestia: ...*sigh*...~ The prince who saved me so many years ago, is he really not coming?
Hestia: Who are you!?
Cecil: Umm, I...
Cecil: Look out!
Cecil: Are you alright? Since I'm here, you don't have to be scared anymore!
Hestia: That phrase...could it be that you're?
Hestia: Damnit, you folks are not getting off easy for this!
Hestia: You...
Cecil: You should be the mermaid I rescued back then, right?
Hestia: You're...my prince!?
Cecil: Thank goodness, you're still alive!
Hestia: My prince!
Cecil: Just call me Cecil, Cecil Hastem.
Hestia: My name is Hestia. Have you forgotten?
Cecil: Ah, right, right, Hestia! It has been seven years since we last met. I've forgotten things...
Hestia: It was ten years, right?
Cecil: Umm, all in all...
Cecil: Today, I'm here to fulfill my promise and have returned to see you.
Hestia: For real!? That's so romantic~~
Hestia: But why did you wait until now to come find me? Did something happen to you in the past few years?
Cecil: Well, something did indeed happen to my family...
Hestia: Then we'll chat about it as we move. Take this as a catch up for the two of us. Let's go!
